Five Brazilians have won the World Cup Golden Boot Award over the years :
Leônidas with 7 goals in 1938 , Ademir with 8 goals in 1950 , Garrincha and Vavá with 4 goals each in 1962 and Ronaldo with 8 goals in 2002 . !
